<class module="chart" runtimeProfile="wb" qualifiedName="javax.baja.chart.AxisRenderer" name="AxisRenderer" packageName="javax.baja.chart" public="true" abstract="true">
<description>
An AxisRenderer handles the drawing of a chart axis.  An axis can be&#xa; renderered as an x axis or a y axis.  An x axis can be renderered&#xa; above the chart area (to the north of it) or below (to the south of&#xa; it).  A y axis can be rendered to the left of the chart area or&#xa; to the right of it.
</description>
